{"tid":1994571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又話黑警死全家，咁個狗仔俾佢個黑警老豆打係唔係抵死？","createTime":"2020-04-29T14:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T00:31:03.000Z","uid":276323,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7430ec7a14cd54ed4e95ca9cb295e82ab91ae6","tid":1994571,"uid":276323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f457bee6cbc0b4fddb3380a46f023ccc3fb1d66","tid":1994571,"uid":16567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"叫下世要小心<br />\n<br />\n唔好再投胎做中國人同黑警家人"},{"pid":"7c41e28abf425697de20deec1e3e2bbc60a00554","tid":1994571,"uid":166308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6c6912d3d2a4e7cdb6e5ed2e1e296b74746957","tid":1994571,"uid":109957,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"希望你唔係五毛假膠<br />\n啱啱都諗到呢個問題，認真答你<br />\n<br />\n首先，如果唔理，黑警繼續打自己個仔<br />\n1)打自己個仔咁狠，打手足咪仲柑<br />\n2)家人keep住忍(走唔到)，無後續後果<br />\n<br />\n要理嘅原因:<br />\n1)可以直接打擊嗰黑警當事人，要承受罰則<br />\n2)抽秤埋藍絲社工，老師<br />\n3)件事發大， 妻離子散，咪有死全家效果<br />\n4)站在道德層面，個細路無得𢵧，佢可能都有憎警察嗰立場<br />\n5)黃絲位道德高地<br />\n6)講黑警衰野又多一樣，打擊藍營士氣<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n理嘅好處多"},{"pid":"22fb7665c3c5d426aff84978d092404a873369ab","tid":1994571,"uid":109957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0f6c6912d3d2a4e7cdb6e5ed2e1e296b74746957","tid":1994571,"uid":109957,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"希望你唔係五毛假膠<br />\n啱啱都諗到呢個問題，認真答你<br />\n<br />\n首先，如果唔理，黑警繼續打自己個仔<br />\n1)打自己個仔咁狠，打手足咪仲柑<br />\n2)家人keep住忍(走唔到)，無後續後果<br />\n<br />\n要理嘅原因:<br />\n1)可以直接打擊嗰黑警當事人，要承受罰則<br />\n2)抽秤埋藍絲社工，老師<br />\n3)件事發大， 妻離子散，咪有死全家效果<br />\n4)站在道德層面，個細路無得𢵧，佢可能都有憎警察嗰立場<br />\n5)黃絲位道德高地<br />\n6)講黑警衰野又多一樣，打擊藍營士氣<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n理嘅好處多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"5)黃絲見弱勢就幫(不論立場)，有道德，並非暴力非理性"},{"pid":"acf3c5a1e9d445be39212581fc879b1b05ee335a","tid":1994571,"uid":55449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"所以咪要公開表彰，<br />\n要發出明確訊息，支持皇軍清除家庭瘀血，<br />\n對自己家屬發動全面嘅思想批鬥，<br />\n清除所有不服從皇軍嘅人，由家庭內部做起！<br />\n<br />\n「制亂先治家，打仔要開花」<br />\n皇軍勁揪！"},{"pid":"4e6bf86872007325e02f6f16fee86b954d47f085","tid":1994571,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"個仔會黃"},{"pid":"1a63375b4e8c9531db8dc853e72717c568ef4360","tid":1994571,"uid":27927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T00:04:54.000Z","msg":"樓主小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑警死全家原來口號嚟<br />\n成個連登都係左膠"},{"pid":"879d6b4a68790759f1e2db87f65b46bcd87cd398","tid":1994571,"uid":120916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f457bee6cbc0b4fddb3380a46f023ccc3fb1d66","tid":1994571,"uid":16567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"叫下世要小心<br />\n<br />\n唔好再投胎做中國人同黑警家人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T00:07:59.000Z","msg":"來生不做支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fb5005dacc5da8bdc11ff10ce8d38020b87d1ce","tid":1994571,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6bf86872007325e02f6f16fee86b954d47f085","tid":1994571,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"個仔會黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T00:09:23.000Z","msg":"連登仔都好撚矛盾下"},{"pid":"a8a4c1e4bda7063872f520bc6e5f12b1c2cf33cf","tid":1994571,"uid":177620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a63375b4e8c9531db8dc853e72717c568ef4360","tid":1994571,"uid":27927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T00:04:54.000Z","msg":"樓主小心<img src=\"/asset